#Led Pulse

## Overview
Example of how to make a Led pulsate like a wave.

## Material
* 01 x Led
* 01 x Arduino
* 02 x Female-male jumper wires

##Circuit
![](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/122277/4789537/5596f712-5dc6-11e4-99d4-4acc53c9ebe8.png)

